{\rtf1\ansi \deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fswiss .VnArial;}}{\colortbl;\red0\green0\blue255;\red255\green255\blue255;\red0\green0\blue0;\red255\green0\blue0;}\deftab1134\plain \f0 \fs22 \i \cf1 \pard\qj \sl220 \par \plain \f0 \fs24 \b \cf1 \pard\qc \sl240 Qu\'c7n Jeans mu\'abn n\'a8m !\plain \f0 \fs24 \cf1 \par \pard\qj \sl240 \par \'a7\'bbng sau nh\'f7ng chi\'d5c qu\'c7n Jeans m\'b5 c\'b8c b\'b9n tr\'ce ng\'b5y nay \'ada th\'ddch l\'b5 c\'b6 m\'e9t l\'dech s\'f6 l\'a9u \'ae\'eai k\'d0o d\'b5i g\'c7n 150 n\'a8m.\par \par Chuy\'d6n b\'bet \'ae\'c7u v\'b5o n\'a8m 1849 khi n\'ad\'edc M\'fc \'aeang ng\'cbp trong c\'acn s\'e8t \'ae\'e6 x\'ab \'aei t\'d7m v\'b5ng. H\'b5ng ng\'b5n d\'a9n nh\'cbp c\'ad \'ae\'e6 v\'d2 mi\'d2n T\'a9y, bang California, v\'edi m\'f4c \'ae\'ddch l\'b5m gi\'c7u b\'bbng c\'b8ch t\'d7m v\'b5ng, h\'e4 \'ae\'ad\'eec g\'e4i l\'b5 "d\'a9n 49", ti\'d5ng l\'e3ng \'b8m ch\'d8 nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai \'ae\'b5o v\'b5ng n\'a8m 1849. Levis Strauss l\'b5 m\'e9t th\'ad\'acng nh\'a9n ng\'ad\'eai \'a7\'f8c c\'f2ng tham gia v\'b8o c\'acn s\'e8t t\'d7m v\'b5ng n\'b5y nh\'adng l\'b9i kh\'abng ph\'b6i l\'b5 "d\'a9n 49". Tuy m\'edi ch\'d8 22 tu\'e6i nh\'adng Levis Strauss \'ae\'b7 l\'b5 ch\'f1 m\'e9t c\'ac s\'eb t\'b9i San Francisco chuy\'aan cung c\'cap c\'b8c lo\'b9i v\'b6i b\'b9t l\'b5m l\'d2u v\'b5 mui che xe ng\'f9a cho d\'a9n t\'d7m v\'b5ng. Qua ti\'d5p x\'f3c v\'edi c\'b8c th\'ee m\'e1, Strauss nh\'cbn th\'cay h\'e4 c\'c7n m\'e9t lo\'b9i qu\'c7n \'ae\'c6c bi\'d6t c\'e3 \'ae\'f1 \'ae\'e9 b\'d2n, ch\'bec v\'b5 c\'e3 th\'d3 ch\'deu \'ae\'ad\'eec s\'f9 h\'b5nh h\'b9 trong nhi\'d2u gi\'ea l\'b5m vi\'d6c li\'aan t\'f4c d\'ad\'edi h\'c7m m\'e1. V\'edi \'ae\'c7u \'e3c kinh doanh nh\'b9y b\'d0n, Levis Strauss \'ae\'b7 d\'efng v\'b6i b\'b9t s\'bdn c\'e3 \'ae\'d3 may nh\'f7ng chi\'d5c qu\'c7n \'ae\'f1 s\'f8c d\'b7i d\'c7u t\'b9i c\'b8c m\'e1 v\'b5ng, \'ae\'e3 l\'b5 nh\'f7ng chi\'d5c qu\'c7n Jeans \'ae\'c7u ti\'aan c\'f1a Strauss. Khi lo\'b9i qu\'c7n b\'bbng v\'b6i b\'b9t b\'bet \'ae\'c7u \'ae\'ad\'eec "d\'a9n 49" \'ada chu\'e9ng c\'f2ng l\'b5 l\'f3c kho v\'b6i c\'f1a Strauss c\'f2ng \'ae\'b7 c\'b9n ki\'d6t. Strauss quy\'d5t \'ae\'denh ch\'e4n lo\'b9i v\'b6i b\'abng d\'b5y nhu\'e9m m\'b5u ch\'b5m \'ae\'d3 may nh\'f7ng chi\'d5c qu\'c7n Jeans mang nh\'b7n hi\'d6u "Levi's". \'a7\'e3 l\'b5 lo\'b9i qu\'c7n Jeans c\'e6 \'aei\'d3n "Levi's 501" m\'b5 cho \'ae\'d5n nay v\'c9n \'ae\'ad\'eec c\'b6 th\'d5 gi\'edi \'ada chu\'e9ng.\par \par Ng\'b5y nay c\'e3 \'ae\'d5n h\'b5ng tr\'a8m nh\'b7n hi\'d6u qu\'c7n  Jeans nh\'ad Lee, Wrangler, Gloria Vanderbilt, Calvin Klein, Versace, Guess, Esprit ... D\'ef sao \'aei n\'f7a, Levi's v\'c9n \'ae\'ad\'eec \'ada chu\'e9ng h\'acn c\'b6. C\'b8c b\'b9n c\'e3 th\'d3 d\'d4 d\'b5ng t\'d7m mua cho m\'d7nh m\'e9t chi\'d5c qu\'c7n Jeans Levi's ch\'ddnh hi\'d6u (genuine Levi's), tuy nhi\'aan c\'e3 m\'e9t s\'e8 \'ae\'c6c \'aei\'d3m c\'c7n ch\'f3 \'fd \'ae\'d3 tr\'b8nh mua ph\'b6i h\'b5ng gi\'b6 nh\'ad sau:\par \par - D\'a9y k\'d0o b\'bbng \'ae\'e5ng kh\'abng g\'d8, kh\'abng b\'de tu\'e9t khi ta c\'c7m \'aeai qu\'c7n k\'d0o sang hai b\'aan. M\'e9t s\'e8 qu\'c7n gi\'b6 m\'c6c m\'e9t th\'eai gian d\'a9y k\'d0o d\'c7n d\'c7n b\'de tu\'e9t xu\'e8ng.\par \par - T\'f3i sau b\'aan ph\'b6i c\'e3 nh\'b7n \'ae\'e1 (red brand tap) ghi ch\'f7 R \'ae\'c6t trong v\'dfng tr\'dfn (Registered - nh\'b7n hi\'d6u \'ae\'b7 \'ae\'a8ng k\'fd).\par \par - N\'d5u qu\'c7n s\'b6n xu\'cat sau n\'a8m 1970, tr\'aan nh\'b7n "LeVI'S" ch\'f7 "e" \'ae\'ad\'eec vi\'d5t d\'ad\'edi d\'b9ng ch\'f7 th\'ad\'eang trong khi nh\'f7ng ch\'f7 c\'dfn l\'b9i nh\'ad "L", "V", "S" \'eb d\'b9ng ch\'f7 in. N\'d5u qu\'c7n s\'b6n xu\'cat tr\'ad\'edc 1970, nh\'b7n "LEVI'S" \'ae\'ad\'eec vi\'d5vie b\'bbng ch\'f7 in.\par \par - \'a7\'e8i v\'edi c\'b8c lo\'b9i Levi's c\'e6 \'aei\'d3n, mi\'d5ng nh\'b7n \'eb l\'adng qu\'c7n ph\'dda sau ngo\'b5i h\'d7nh v\'cf hai con ng\'f9a k\'d0o qu\'c7n Jeans c\'dfn ph\'b6i c\'e3 s\'e8 s\'aa-ri (series number). V\'dd d\'f4 nh\'ad LeVI'S 501.\par \par - D\'a9y k\'d0o c\'e3 d\'cau "zxx", \'ae\'e8i v\'edi qu\'c7n c\'b5i c\'f3c th\'d7 tr\'aan m\'e7i c\'f3c c\'e3 d\'cau "xx". \par \par - Ngo\'b5i ra c\'dfn r\'cat nhi\'d2u \'ae\'c6c \'aei\'d3m kh\'b8c gi\'f3p b\'b9n c\'e3 th\'d3 ph\'a9n bi\'d6t nh\'ad ch\'cat v\'b6i, \'ae\'ad\'eang may v.v...\par \par Lo\'b9i "LeVI'S 501" v\'b5  "LeVI'S 501s" (li-vai 501) l\'b5 Jeans c\'e6 \'aei\'d3n (classic jeans), c\'e3 d\'b8ng r\'cat \'ae\'d1p. C\'e3 th\'d3 t\'d7m mua t\'b9i c\'b8c shop th\'eai trang v\'edi gi\'b8 t\'f5 500.000 \'ae - 580.000 \'ae \'ae\'e8i v\'edi qu\'c7n SX t\'b9i M\'fc v\'b5 t\'f5 200.000 \'ae - 220.000 \'ae n\'d5u SX t\'b9i Hongkong.\par \par V\'d7 h\'d7nh d\'b8ng v\'b5 m\'b5u s\'bec c\'f1a qu\'c7n Jeans r\'cat quan tr\'e4ng, n\'aan khi gi\'c6t c\'b8c b\'b9n c\'c7n l\'adu \'fd:\par \par - Tr\'ad\'edc khi gi\'c6t, l\'e9n tr\'b8i m\'c6t trong ra ngo\'b5i \'ae\'d3 \'ae\'ec b\'de phai m\'b5u.\par \par - \'a7\'e3ng d\'a9y k\'d0o, c\'b8i c\'f3c qu\'c7n tr\'ad\'edc khi cho v\'b5o m\'b8y gi\'c6t \'ae\'d3 gi\'f7 nguy\'aan d\'b8ng qu\'c7n.\par \par - Khi ph\'aci, k\'d1p l\'adng qu\'c7n tr\'aan m\'bec \'b8o theo su\'e8t chi\'d2u d\'b5i, kh\'abng v\'bet tr\'aan m\'bec \'b8o.\par \par V\'b5 cu\'e8i c\'efng l\'b5 l\'eai khuy\'aan d\'b5nh cho c\'b8c b\'b9n n\'f7 c\'e3 b\'f4ng d\'ad\'edi h\'aci to l\'b5 kh\'abng n\'aan m\'c6c qu\'c7n  Jeans trong m\'e9t th\'eai gian qu\'b8 d\'b5i v\'d7 s\'f9 b\'e3 s\'b8t c\'f1a \'ae\'f2ng qu\'c7n c\'e9ng th\'aam k\'d0m tho\'b8ng kh\'dd s\'cf g\'a9y \'b6nh h\'ad\'ebng kh\'abng t\'e8t.\plain \f0 \fs24 \par \par \plain \f0 \fs24 \b \cf4 \pard\qc \sl240 LONG LIVE BLUE JEANS\plain \f0 \fs24 \i \par }